# README

## Introduction

This is a Django and React app that uses the OpenAI API to
summarize Congressional data.

## Requirements

- Python 3.x
- Django
- React
- OpenAI package (can be installed via pip)

## Installation

1. Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/yourrepo.git

2. Install the requirements

pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Run the migrations

python manage.py migrate

4. Start the development server

5. In a separate terminal, navigate to the `frontend` directory and start the React development server

cd frontend
npm start

6. Go to http://localhost:3000/ in your browser to view the app.

## Usage

1. Enter a URL in the input field
2. Click the "Summarize" button
3. The summarized text will appear below the button.

## Note

Make sure you have a openai api key, if not create it and add it to the settings





